T02TD1374E:250b-1: sha dangga yo ga au pa de sha /
T02TD1374E:250b-3: yan lag drug gi sbyor ba'i man ngag //
T02TD1374E:250b-4: dpal mad bde ba chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1374E:250b-5: bde chen sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1374E:250b-6: sbyor drug man nga bshad par bya //
T02TD1374E:250b-7: sgrub po dbang bzhi thob pa yi //
T02TD1374E:250b-8: rdo rje 'chang chen sgrub don du //
T02TD1374E:250b-9: dben pa'i gnas su 'bol stan la //
T02TD1374E:250b-10: yi dam ltar gnas sbyor drug bsgom //
T02TD1374E:250b-11: dang po so sor sdud pa ni //
T02TD1374E:250b-12: mtshan mo sngon la nyin mo phyi //
T02TD1374E:250b-13: bu ga med la thog mtho'i nang //
T02TD1374E:250b-14: ri rab bsrangs la gling bzhi bsdu //
T02TD1374E:250b-15: gyen la nyi zla dar lce bskyod //
T02TD1374E:250b-16: rdo rje spyi pas rgya mtsho gzhom //
T02TD1374E:250b-17: steng gi rlung chen thur la brdeg /
T02TD1374E:250b-18: lus kyi byed pa zhes bya ste //
T02TD1374E:250b-19: des ni rlung rnams nang du 'ching //
T02TD1374E:250b-20: gtsug tor chen po'i lta stangs bya //
T02TD1374E:250b-21: lha yi nga rgyal gnas pa yis //
T02TD1374E:250b-22: nam mkha' zhen pas nam mkhar blta //
T02TD1374E:250b-23: du ba la sogs rtags lnga 'byung //
T02TD1374E:250b-25: nyin mo nang du nub shar ba blta //
T02TD1374E:250b-26: gung la bsgom par mi bya'o //
T02TD1374E:250b-27: snga ma ltar ni byed bcings pas //
T02TD1374E:250b-28: phyi yi mkha' la rtog med blta //
T02TD1374E:250b-30: rig pa mkha'i lding la sogs rtags //
T02TD1374E:250b-31: so sor sdud la snyoms zhugs na //
T02TD1374E:250b-32: sngags rnams kun gyi byin gyis rlob //
T02TD1374E:250b-33: stong nyid de brtan bya ba'i phyir //
T02TD1374E:250b-34: bsam gtan snga ma ltar ni bsgom //
T02TD1374E:250b-35: nam mkhar mig lta stong nyid bsgom //
T02TD1374E:250b-36: nge la goms pas shes rab dang //
T02TD1374E:250b-37: rtog dang dpyod dang dga' bde 'byung //
T02TD1374E:250b-39: bsam gtan la ni snyoms zhugs na /
T02TD1374E:250b-41: rig pa rtse gcig sogs rgyur 'gyur //
T02TD1374E:250b-42: de gnyis thog mar dge ba ste //
T02TD1374E:250b-43: stong nyid mthong rten byed pa'o //
T02TD1374E:250b-44: stong la bde ba rgyas gdab phyir //
T02TD1374E:250b-45: srog dang rtsol bas rlung dbang sdud //
T02TD1374E:250b-46: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i lta stangs bya //
T02TD1374E:250b-47: kun 'dar nang du dbyugs bcug la //
T02TD1374E:250b-48: rdo rje'i bzlas pa brtsams par bya //
T02TD1374E:250b-49: des ni bde ba rab skyes na //
T02TD1374E:250b-50: gtum mo 'bar ba'i sbyor ba bya //
T02TD1374E:250b-51: shin tu ma skyes phyag rgyar sbyar //
T02TD1374E:250b-52: lus sems bde ba chen por nges //
T02TD1374E:250b-53: sangs rgyas sras dang mkha' 'gro mthong //
T02TD1374E:250b-56: sog dang rtsol bas nges par ni //
T02TD1374E:250b-57: byang chub sems sogs rnam ni gzigs //
T02TD1374E:251a-2: 'khor lo bzhi yi lte ba la //
T02TD1374E:251a-3: rlung sogs za mi dang btsud bsgom //
T02TD1374E:251a-4: lus yang la sogs rtags 'byung ngo //
T02TD1374E:251a-5: bum gnas la sogs dgu ru 'gyur //
T02TD1374E:251a-6: rtag tu 'dzin pa'i stobs kyis ni //
T02TD1374E:251a-7: rdo rje sems dpa' yang dag 'jug / de gnyis bar du dge ba'o //
T02TD1374E:251a-8: bde stong dbyer med brtan bya'i phyir //
T02TD1374E:251a-9: rjes su dran pa bsgom pa ni //
T02TD1374E:251a-10: gnas bzhir brtan pa'i bde stong bsgom //
T02TD1374E:251a-11: shin tu goms byas sangs rgyas kyi //
T02TD1374E:251a-12: lta ba mi 'phro brtan par gnas //
T02TD1374E:251a-14: rjes dran la ni snyoms zhugs na //
T02TD1374E:251a-16: rjes med la sogs sku shes bya //
T02TD1374E:251a-17: de brtan bya phyir ting 'dzin bsgom //
T02TD1374E:251a-18: bde stong dbyed [?] med de nyid la //
T02TD1374E:251a-19: shin tu goms par bya ba'o //
T02TD1374E:251a-20: thams cad bde stong la sogs 'byung //
T02TD1374E:251a-21: lhun grub la sogs dgu ru 'gyur //
T02TD1374E:251a-22: ting 'dzin dbang sgyur tsam gyis ni //
T02TD1374E:251a-24: de gnyis tha mar dge ba'o //
T02TD1374E:251a-25: de la spyod pa goms pa yis //
T02TD1374E:251a-26: tshe 'di nyid du sangs rgyas thob //
T02TD1374E:251a-27: ma thob par do'i sbyor drug bsgom //
T02TD1374E:251a-28: de ni chags bral man ngag ste //
T02TD1374E:251a-29: chags can sbyor drug gzhan du shes //
T02TD1374E:251a-30: de byas dge bas bdag dang gzhan //
T02TD1374E:251a-31: rdo rje 'chang chen gnas thob shog / sbyor ba yan lag drug gi man ngag tse lu pas mdzad ba rdzogs so /
T02TD1374E:251a-34: lo ts'a ba rva chos rab kyis bsgyur ba'o//
